## Conventions

- Master branch `master`
- Work based on [Jira](https://blazemeter.atlassian.net) tickets
- Pull request branch name [**should**](https://github.com/Blazemeter/a.blazemeter.com/blob/develop/tools/hooks/commit-msg) reference one or more tickets
- Search our [wiki](https://blazemeter.atlassian.net/wiki) or [Jira](https://blazemeter.atlassian.net) for more insights

