## Python virtual environments

- Create venv
```
$ python3 -m venv ./venv
```
- Use venv
```
$ source ./venv/bin/activate
 ...
$ deactivate # optional
```
- Install requirements
```
$ python -m pip install -r requirements.txt # once
 ... or ...
$ pip install ...
```

